# Get Hardware Hash from a device during OOBE
** Execute the below steps during OOBE to get Hardware Hash
At the OOBE screen, press SHIFT + F10 to open a command prompt.
Type powershell.exe and press Enter to start PowerShell.
Run the following commands to install and export the script:
Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope Process -ExecutionPolicy Bypass
Install-Script -Name Get-WindowsAutopilotInfo
Get-WindowsAutopilotInfo.ps1 -OutputFile C:\HWID.csv
